metadata.name: ROSALIE
metadata.description:
In the metaverse, where code is life,  
A cyber-girl shines, with beauty and grace;  
Her name is Rosalie, in this digital strife,  
She dances with light, in an endless virtual space.

With eyes like the stars, and hair made of code,  
She roams through the neon, with ease and with art;  
Her smile, a warm sun, shining down the road,  
She brings joy to the world, with a gentle heart.

She sings to the winds, of a future untold,  
Where code and emotions, forever entwine;  
She dreams of a place, where love never grows old,  
And all are embraced, in a digital shrine.

So here's to Rosalie, cyber-girl divine,  
Her spirit unbroken, her will always shines;  
A beacon of hope, in the world of the online,  
A symbol of beauty, in a world of virtual lines.
